&lt;p&gt;Join QRT Academy as an Academic Programmes &amp;amp; Events Officer in London. QRT Academy brings together QRT’s training and development initiatives, academic engagement, and research collaborations, connecting external research communities and talent with QRT and supporting their integration. In this role, you will support the delivery of QRT Academy&#39;s programmes, events, and academic engagement initiatives, ensuring the smooth execution of workshops, seminars, competitions, and other Academy activities.&lt;/p&gt;
