&lt;li&gt;Strong project management and stakeholder management skills, with the ability to coordinate complex initiatives across multiple teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Good understanding of electronic trading workflows, exchange connectivity, market access and front-to-back trading processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with low-latency trading environments, co-location or trading infrastructure concepts.&lt;/li&gt;
